## 6. Functional Flow

```
gateTypeL_Tasks()
│
├─ 1. Debounce Switch A
│       rawSwitchA = digitalRead(switchPinA)
│       On raw change → reset lLastDebounceA
│       After lDebounceDelayA (35 ms) → lStableReadingA = lLastReadingA
│       switchA = (lStableReadingA == LOW)
│
├─ 2. Read Switch B (raw, no debounce)
│       switchB = (digitalRead(switchPinB) == LOW)
│
├─ 3. Sync gate-close state with limit switch
│       checkSwitchState()
│
├─ 4. if switchA == true  (Switch A ON → stepper open/hold path)
│   │
│   ├─ Reset close state machine:
│   │     belowTriggerStart = 0
│   │     notClosedStart = 0
│   │     closeLatchedForLowSignal = false
│   │
│   ├─ if gateOpenState != true
│   │     openGate()
│   │
│   └─ else (gate already open → refresh hold)
│         gateOpenTime = millis()
│         digitalWrite(reedRelayPin, HIGH)
│         gateOpenState = true
│         trace = "OPEN"
│         displayStat()
│         startTime = 0
│         digitalWrite(enablePin, HIGH)
│         setGateState(STATE_OPEN)
│
├─ 5. else  (Switch A OFF → A/B/C/D-style close state machine)
│   │
│   ├─ 5a. Start delay window timer
│   │       if belowTriggerStart == 0:
│   │           belowTriggerStart = millis()
│   │           notClosedStart = 0
│   │           closeLatchedForLowSignal = false
│   │
│   ├─ 5b. Not-closed debounce timer
│   │       if gateCloseState == false AND notClosedStart == 0:
│   │           notClosedStart = millis()
│   │       if gateCloseState == true:
│   │           notClosedStart = 0
│   │
│   ├─ 5c. Compute eligibility
│   │       gateIndicatesOpen      = gateOpenState || gateState∈{STATE_OPEN,STATE_OPENING}
│   │       closeInProgress        = startTime != 0 || gateState == STATE_CLOSING
│   │       gatePhysicallyNotClosed = notClosedStart != 0
│   │                                 && (millis() - notClosedStart) >= notClosedDebounceMs
│   │       eligibleToStartClose   = (gateIndicatesOpen || gatePhysicallyNotClosed)
│   │                                 && (millis() - belowTriggerStart >= lowSignalCloseDelayMs)
│   │                                 && closeLatchedForLowSignal == false
│   │
│   ├─ 5d. Issue close if in-progress or newly eligible
│   │       if closeInProgress || eligibleToStartClose:
│   │           if eligibleToStartClose:
│   │               closeLatchedForLowSignal = true
│   │           closeGate()
│   │
│   ├─ 5e. Suppress re-trigger once confirmed closed
│   │       if gateState == STATE_CLOSED && gateCloseState == true:
│   │           closeLatchedForLowSignal = true
│   │
│   └─ 5f. Hold delay
│           delay(holdTime)
│
├─ 6. Servo B edge detection & command
│       if switchB != (lastSwitchBState == LOW):
│           lastSwitchBState = switchB ? LOW : HIGH
│           if switchB:  servoB.write(openB)
│           else:        servoB.write(closedB)
│
└─ 7. OTA service
        ArduinoOTA.handle()
```

