## 7. State Machine — Stepper Close Path (Switch A OFF)

| Condition | Action |
|---|---|
| `belowTriggerStart == 0` | Start delay-window timer; reset `notClosedStart` and latch |
| `gateCloseState == false` AND `notClosedStart == 0` | Start not-closed debounce timer |
| `gateCloseState == true` | Reset not-closed debounce timer |
| `eligibleToStartClose == true` | Set latch, call `closeGate()` |
| `closeInProgress == true` AND latch already set | Continue calling `closeGate()` each iteration |
| `gateState == STATE_CLOSED` AND `gateCloseState == true` | Set latch to suppress further triggers |
| `switchA` goes HIGH | Reset all close-path state (`belowTriggerStart`, `notClosedStart`, latch) |

